      • sendReport

        public boolean sendReport​(java.lang.String name,
                          java.lang.String report)
        Sends POST request to Pastebin web API to create paste containing given report.

        Paste created with paste name " Report"

        Returns false if name or report is null or empty.

        Parameters:
        name - Name of character that the report is about
        report - String representation of report data to create paste with
        Returns:
        boolean - return true if report sent and URL to paste retrieved, otherwise false
